  m_Name: TakasuHaruko
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::CharacterInfo
  characterName: Takasu Haruko
  description: The first and the oldest of the Takasu sisters... by about six minutes.
    Takasu Haruko is the smartest of the triplets. Well, she isn't that smart, since
    she's one of the lower performing students of the class. But she's always trying
    to help her sisters just barely pass their exams. She's also formed a weird antagonistic
    relationship with her English teacher, since she gets bugged by her the most.
    It's hard to blame her when she's just doing everything she can to fit in.
